---
title: Mini Christmas Ham & Sides with Chocolate Brownies for Dessert
description: Enjoy a celebratory meal of Christmas classics – ham, roasted spuds and bright greens with some extra-special touches – without hours in the kitchen or weeks of leftovers. And for the ultimate sweet finish, whip up an easy pan of brownies.

 *See the separate recipe card for the brownie recipe.*
